  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_2_1",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_male_intro_part1.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "比如现在，教学楼的轮廓线在轻微地\"融化\"，",
    "next": "male_intro_2_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_2_2",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_male_intro_part1.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "就像夏日柏油路上的热浪，",
    "next": "male_intro_2_3"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_2_3",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_male_intro_part1.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "可今天明明是个秋高气爽的日子。",
    "next": "male_intro_3_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_3_1",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_male_intro_part2.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "祖父常说，我们家的人能看到\"世界的另一面\"。",
    "next": "male_intro_3_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_3_2",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_male_intro_part2.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "以前我只当是故事，",
