  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_3_3",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_male_intro_part2.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "但自从他把那本《星图异闻录》留给我之后，",
    "next": "male_intro_3_4"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_3_4",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_male_intro_part2.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "这种\"异常\"就越来越频繁了……",
